                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080601-70-defend590 t18080601-70-punish401"></join>
               Fined One Shilling
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
